<body>
    <h1><b>FIVE MATHEMATICAL SYMBOLS</b></h1>
    <li>Addition: &plus;</li>
    <li>Subtraction: &minus;</li>
    <li>Multiplication: &times;</li>
    <li>Division: &divide;</li>
    <li>Square root: &radic;</li>

</body>
